But no, actually I am not trying to get hourly results. I am trying to get results grouped by **hour of day**.

The example above based on the Wikipedia example data set may not be clear, because that data set only contains data for a single day. Consider this alternate example data set: 

```
{"timestamp": "2013-08-29T01:02:33Z", "page": "Gypsy Danger", "added": 57, "deleted": 200, "delta": -143}
